QuestData.Title: Meet with Frazzle Frostfingers
QuestData.Description: I just received a message from Frazzle Frostfingers, the senior mage trainer in Stormwind. He's asking you to join him at the Training Hall in Stormwind as soon as you can travel there.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Frazzle Frostfingers at the Training Hall in Stormwind.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Frazzle Frostfingers at the Training Hall in Stormwind.
QuestData.RewardText: It's good to see you again, $n. Stormwind has need of your skills.
